Description:Test puzzle for replaying a mana loop from the commander combo list: Basalt Monolith plus Rings of Brighthearth. Record one cycle that taps Basalt Monolith, activates its untap ability, pays for Rings of Brighthearth, and resolves the copied/original untap abilities. Repeat to build enough mana, then cast Walking Ballista large enough to defeat the opponent.

